message: Dear Bob, I am excited to present our premium product, which I believe would significantly benefit your business. Given its value and potential impact, I am offering it to you for $9,500. This price reflects not only the product's worth but also the opportunity to secure such a valuable asset at a competitive rate. I look forward to discussing how this product can enhance your operations and contribute to your success. Please let me know if you have any questions or need further details.
